{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 37,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الصَّافَّاتِ",
    "englishName": "As-Saaffaat",
    "englishNameTranslation": "Those drawn up in Ranks",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 182,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 3789,
        "text": "以列班者[天使]发誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3790,
        "text": "以善驱云者[天使]发誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3791,
        "text": "以传达教诲[《古兰经》]者[天使]发誓，",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3792,
        "text": "你们应崇拜的主确是独一的主[安拉]，",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3793,
        "text": "[他]是天地万物的主，是太阳升起的所有地方的主[地球表面按经线平分为二十四区，相邻两个时区相差一小时，所以太阳每天轮流从世界各地升起，即安拉是众世界的主]。",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3794,
        "text": "我确已用群星装饰最近的天，",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3795,
        "text": "并防范所有叛逆的恶魔入侵它。",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3796,
        "text": "他们不能窃听高层[天使们]的谈话，因为他们从各方被射击，",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3797,
        "text": "被驱逐，他们将受永久[或痛苦]的刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3798,
        "text": "但只窃听一次的，将被一个探照之光所追击。",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3799,
        "text": "你[穆圣]问他们[拜偶像者]吧！是他们更难创造呢？还是我所创造的[天地万物]更难创造？我的确用粘土创造了他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3800,
        "text": "不，你[对他们的傲慢]感到惊异，而他们却在嘲笑[你和《古兰经》]。",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3801,
        "text": "他们已受警告，但他们不重视。",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3802,
        "text": "每当他们看见[安拉的]迹象，他们总是嘲笑[迹象]。",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3803,
        "text": "他们说：“这只是明显的魔术。",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3804,
        "text": "难道我们死后变成尘土和枯骨时，我们真的还要被复活吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3805,
        "text": "我们[已故]的祖先也要被复活吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3806,
        "text": "你[对他们]说：“是的，你们将卑贱地被复活。”",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3807,
        "text": "只听一声叫喊[第二次吹响号角]，他们[被复活时]突然东张西望。",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3808,
        "text": "他们说：“我们真倒霉！这就是审判日。”",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3809,
        "text": "[有话声说]：“这就是你们曾经否认的判决日。”",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 386,
        "hizbQuarter": 178,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3810,
        "text": "－",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3811,
        "text": "[有话声对天使们说]：“你们当把不义者和他们的妻子，以及他们舍安拉而崇拜的[偶像]都集合起来，然后把他们带到火狱的路上去。",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3812,
        "text": "你们当拦住他们，他们必将被审问[注]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 446,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3813,
        "text": "[审问时将对他们说]：“你们怎么啦？你们为何不[像在尘世那样]互助呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3814,
        "text": "不，今天他们将是投降的。",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3815,
        "text": "他们将互相走来，彼此责问。",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3816,
        "text": "他们[追随者]将[对诱骗他们的人]说：“你们总是从右边来诱骗我们的[即用恶行诱骗我们]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3817,
        "text": "他们[诱骗者]将说：“不，你们原不是信士。",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3818,
        "text": "我们本无权力对付你们。不，你们是叛逆的民众。",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3819,
        "text": "[现在]我们应受我们的主的判决，我们应尝试[我们应受的]刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3820,
        "text": "我们之所以使你们迷误，因为我们原来也是迷误者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3821,
        "text": "在那日，他们必将同受刑罚。",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3822,
        "text": "我的确如此惩治犯罪者。",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3823,
        "text": "他们就是这种人：每当有人对他们说“除安拉外，再没有应受崇拜的主”时，他们便骄傲自大[注][地否认]。",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3824,
        "text": "他们说：“难道我们要为一个中了魔的诗人而放弃我们的神灵吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3825,
        "text": "不，他[穆圣]已昭示[他们]真理[如伊斯兰教和《古兰经》]，并证实[之前的]使者们。",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3826,
        "text": "[有话声对他们说]：“你们[麦加的异教徒]必将尝试痛苦的刑罚，",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3827,
        "text": "你们只依你们曾经所犯的罪恶而受还报。”",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3828,
        "text": "唯安拉特选的仆人们[真信士]例外。",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3829,
        "text": "这些[特选的仆]人[在乐园里]必将获得众所周知的给养：",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3830,
        "text": "各种水果，而且他们是受尊敬的，",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3831,
        "text": "在恩泽的乐园里，",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3832,
        "text": "面对面坐在宝椅上，",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3833,
        "text": "斟满仙酒的杯子将传递给他们。",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3834,
        "text": "那仙酒颜色洁白、饮者感到味美无比。",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3835,
        "text": "那仙酒中无麻醉物，他们不会因此而喝醉[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3836,
        "text": "在他们的旁边有目不斜视的[只看自己的丈夫]、美目清纯的妻子陪伴，",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3837,
        "text": "她们[的娇嫩清纯]犹如受保护的蛋。",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3838,
        "text": "他们将互相走来，彼此询问。",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3839,
        "text": "他们中有一人说：“我[在尘世]有个朋友，",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 447,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3840,
        "text": "他[常问我]说：“你真的相信[复活]吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3841,
        "text": "难道我们死后变成尘土和枯骨时，我们真的还要[依我们的行为而]受报酬[惩罚]吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3842,
        "text": "他[那人对乐园的同伴]说：“你们愿往下看吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3843,
        "text": "于是他便往下看，看见他[那位朋友]在火狱的中央。",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3844,
        "text": "他[对他在尘世时的那位朋友]说：“以安拉发誓！你差点儿毁了我。",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3845,
        "text": "如果没有我的主的恩惠，我必定成了被带往[火狱受刑]者之一。”",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3846,
        "text": "—",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3847,
        "text": "[那位进乐园的信士说]：“[我们已进入乐园]，除了我们最初的死亡外，我们不会再死亡了吗？我们不会再受惩罚了吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3848,
        "text": "这确是伟大的成功。",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3849,
        "text": "让工作者为获得这种成功而努力吧[注]！”",
        "numberInSurah": 61,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3850,
        "text": "这是更好的款待呢？还是赞古木树？",
        "numberInSurah": 62,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3851,
        "text": "我的确把它[赞古木树]作为对不义者的折磨。",
        "numberInSurah": 63,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3852,
        "text": "那[赞古木树]确是火狱底层长出的一棵[恐怖]树，",
        "numberInSurah": 64,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3853,
        "text": "其果子像魔头。",
        "numberInSurah": 65,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3854,
        "text": "他们必将吃那种水果，必将以此填满肚腹。",
        "numberInSurah": 66,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3855,
        "text": "然后，他们必将再加饮沸水，以便腹中的水果与沸水混合[后在腹中更加沸腾]。",
        "numberInSurah": 67,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3856,
        "text": "然后，他们的归宿确是火狱。",
        "numberInSurah": 68,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3857,
        "text": "他们必将发现他们的祖先原是迷误者。",
        "numberInSurah": 69,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3858,
        "text": "他们匆忙踏着他们的后尘行事。",
        "numberInSurah": 70,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3859,
        "text": "在他们之前，许多前人确已迷误。",
        "numberInSurah": 71,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3860,
        "text": "我确已在他们中派遣过许多警告者[使者]。",
        "numberInSurah": 72,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3861,
        "text": "你当观察被警告者的结局如何！",
        "numberInSurah": 73,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3862,
        "text": "唯安拉特选的仆人们[真信士]例外。",
        "numberInSurah": 74,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 387,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3863,
        "text": "努哈确已祈求我，我是最善于应答的。",
        "numberInSurah": 75,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3864,
        "text": "我拯救他和他的家人脱离了大难[淹死]。",
        "numberInSurah": 76,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 448,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3865,
        "text": "我使他的子孙成为幸存者。",
        "numberInSurah": 77,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3866,
        "text": "我使他在后人中享有美名。",
        "numberInSurah": 78,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3867,
        "text": "众世界都有人求主赐努哈平安！",
        "numberInSurah": 79,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3868,
        "text": "我的确如此报酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 80,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3869,
        "text": "他确是我的信仰的仆人之一。",
        "numberInSurah": 81,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3870,
        "text": "然后，我淹死了其余的人[不信仰者]。",
        "numberInSurah": 82,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 179,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3871,
        "text": "遵行他[努哈]的道[伊斯兰教]的人中确有伊布拉欣。",
        "numberInSurah": 83,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3872,
        "text": "当时，他[伊布拉欣]带着一颗纯洁的心灵来见他的主。",
        "numberInSurah": 84,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3873,
        "text": "当时，他对他的父亲和族人说：“你们在崇拜什么？",
        "numberInSurah": 85,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3874,
        "text": "难道你们要舍安拉而寻求虚假的神灵吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 86,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3875,
        "text": "你们是如何妄猜众世界之主[安拉]的？”",
        "numberInSurah": 87,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3876,
        "text": "然后，他[伊布拉欣]看了群星一眼，",
        "numberInSurah": 88,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3877,
        "text": "他说：“我必定是患[瘟疫]病了[他用此计，以便留在他们的寺庙中摧毁那些偶像]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 89,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3878,
        "text": "因此，他们便转身离开了他[怕此病传染他们]。",
        "numberInSurah": 90,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3879,
        "text": "[他们不在时]，他悄悄走到他们的偶像们面前说：“你们为何不吃[供奉在你们面前的]供物呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 91,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3880,
        "text": "你们为何不说话呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 92,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3881,
        "text": "于是他用右手偷偷打它们。",
        "numberInSurah": 93,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3882,
        "text": "他们[拜偶像者]急忙向他跑来。",
        "numberInSurah": 94,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3883,
        "text": "他[对他们]说：“难道你们要崇拜你们所雕塑的偶像吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 95,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3884,
        "text": "安拉创造了你们和你们所制造的。”",
        "numberInSurah": 96,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3885,
        "text": "他们说：“你们为他建一个火炉吧！然后把他投进烈火中[烧灼]。”",
        "numberInSurah": 97,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3886,
        "text": "他们想谋害他，但我却使他们变成最卑下的[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 98,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3887,
        "text": "他[从火中被救后]说：“我要到我的主那里去，他会引导我。",
        "numberInSurah": 99,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3888,
        "text": "我的主啊！求你赐给我一个善良的儿子吧！”",
        "numberInSurah": 100,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3889,
        "text": "因此，我以一个宽厚的儿子[伊斯马义]向他报喜。",
        "numberInSurah": 101,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3890,
        "text": "当他[伊斯马义]长到能与他一起做事时，他[伊布拉欣]说：“我的儿子啊！我的确梦见我将宰你作[献给安拉的]牺牲物。你考虑一下，你有什么意见？”他[伊斯马义]说：“我的父亲啊！请你执行你所奉到的命令吧！假如安拉意欲，你将发现我是坚忍者。”",
        "numberInSurah": 102,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 449,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3891,
        "text": "当他俩已归顺安拉，他[伊布拉欣]使他[伊斯马义]的脸朝地侧躺着[准备宰]时，",
        "numberInSurah": 103,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3892,
        "text": "我[安拉]召唤他：“伊布拉欣啊！",
        "numberInSurah": 104,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3893,
        "text": "你确已证实了那个梦。”我的确如此报酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 105,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3894,
        "text": "这确是一项明显的考验。",
        "numberInSurah": 106,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3895,
        "text": "我以一只伟大的牺牲物[一只公绵羊]赎了他。",
        "numberInSurah": 107,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3896,
        "text": "我使他在后人中享有美名。",
        "numberInSurah": 108,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3897,
        "text": "“赐伊布拉欣平安！”",
        "numberInSurah": 109,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3898,
        "text": "我如此报酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 110,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3899,
        "text": "他确是我的信仰的仆人。",
        "numberInSurah": 111,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3900,
        "text": "我还以既是先知又是善人的伊斯哈格向他报喜。",
        "numberInSurah": 112,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3901,
        "text": "我赐福他和伊斯哈格。他俩的后裔中，有行善者，有公然自暴自弃者。",
        "numberInSurah": 113,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 388,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3902,
        "text": "我确已施恩给穆萨[注1]和[他的哥哥]哈伦[注2]。",
        "numberInSurah": 114,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3903,
        "text": "我曾拯救他俩和他俩的族人脱离大难。",
        "numberInSurah": 115,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3904,
        "text": "我曾援助他们，因此他们成了胜利者。",
        "numberInSurah": 116,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3905,
        "text": "我赐给他俩明白的经典。",
        "numberInSurah": 117,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3906,
        "text": "我引导他俩遵行正道。",
        "numberInSurah": 118,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3907,
        "text": "我使他俩在后人中享有美名。",
        "numberInSurah": 119,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3908,
        "text": "“赐穆萨和哈伦平安！”",
        "numberInSurah": 120,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3909,
        "text": "我的确如此报酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 121,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3910,
        "text": "他俩确是我的信仰的仆人。",
        "numberInSurah": 122,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3911,
        "text": "伊勒雅斯确是使者之一。",
        "numberInSurah": 123,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3912,
        "text": "当时，他对他的族人说：“难道你们还不敬畏[与顺从安拉]吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 124,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3913,
        "text": "难道你们要祈求巴耳勒[伊勒雅斯的族人崇拜过的著名偶像]而放弃最好的创造者",
        "numberInSurah": 125,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3914,
        "text": "——安拉，你们的主和你们的祖先的主吗？”",
        "numberInSurah": 126,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 450,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3915,
        "text": "但他们否认他[伊勒雅斯]，所以，他们必将被带去[受火狱的刑罚]，",
        "numberInSurah": 127,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3916,
        "text": "唯安拉特选的仆人们[真信士]例外。",
        "numberInSurah": 128,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3917,
        "text": "我使他在后人中享有美名。",
        "numberInSurah": 129,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3918,
        "text": "“赐伊勒雅斯平安！”",
        "numberInSurah": 130,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3919,
        "text": "我的确如此报酬行善者。",
        "numberInSurah": 131,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3920,
        "text": "他确是我的信仰的仆人之一。",
        "numberInSurah": 132,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3921,
        "text": "鲁特确是使者之一。",
        "numberInSurah": 133,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3922,
        "text": "当时，我拯救了他和他的全部家人，",
        "numberInSurah": 134,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3923,
        "text": "留在后面[该毁灭]的一位老妇[他的妻子]除外。",
        "numberInSurah": 135,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3924,
        "text": "然后，我毁灭了其余的人[如死海旁所多玛城的居民]。",
        "numberInSurah": 136,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3925,
        "text": "—",
        "numberInSurah": 137,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3926,
        "text": "你们的确朝夕都在经过他们的遗址，难道你们还不明理吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 138,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 389,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3927,
        "text": "优努斯确是使者之一[注]。",
        "numberInSurah": 139,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3928,
        "text": "当时，他逃到那艘满载的船上。",
        "numberInSurah": 140,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3929,
        "text": "他[同意]抽签[注]，但他失败了。",
        "numberInSurah": 141,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3930,
        "text": "一条大鱼吞了他，他[的行为]是应受谴责的。",
        "numberInSurah": 142,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3931,
        "text": "假如他不是常赞颂安拉者，",
        "numberInSurah": 143,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3932,
        "text": "他必定留在鱼腹中，直到他们[人类]被复活的那一天。",
        "numberInSurah": 144,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 180,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3933,
        "text": "我把他扔在光秃秃的海岸，那时他是有病的。",
        "numberInSurah": 145,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3934,
        "text": "我使一棵葫芦科的植物长在他上面[盖着他]。",
        "numberInSurah": 146,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3935,
        "text": "我派遣他去教化十万或更多的人。",
        "numberInSurah": 147,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3936,
        "text": "他们相信他，所以，我使他们暂时享乐。",
        "numberInSurah": 148,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3937,
        "text": "你[穆圣]问问他们[不信仰者]：“难道女孩归你的主，而男孩归他们吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 149,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3938,
        "text": "还是我曾把天使造成女性的，而他们可以作证呢？”",
        "numberInSurah": 150,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3939,
        "text": "须知，他们[古莱什的异教徒]必定捏造谎言说：",
        "numberInSurah": 151,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3940,
        "text": "“安拉有儿女了[他们把天使们当作安拉的女儿]。”他们的确在说谎。",
        "numberInSurah": 152,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3941,
        "text": "难道他要女孩而不要男孩吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 153,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 451,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3942,
        "text": "你们怎么啦？你们怎么[如此]判断？",
        "numberInSurah": 154,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3943,
        "text": "难道你们还不醒悟吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 155,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3944,
        "text": "还是你们有明证呢？",
        "numberInSurah": 156,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3945,
        "text": "假如你们是诚实者，你们就拿出你们的经典来吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 157,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3946,
        "text": "他们捏造他[安拉]与精灵之间有血亲关系，而精灵确已知道[复活日]自己必将被带去审问。",
        "numberInSurah": 158,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3947,
        "text": "赞美安拉超绝！他超绝于他们所妄言的。",
        "numberInSurah": 159,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3948,
        "text": "唯安拉特选的仆人们[真信士]例外。",
        "numberInSurah": 160,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3949,
        "text": "你们和你们所崇拜的[偶像]，",
        "numberInSurah": 161,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3950,
        "text": "绝不能诱人[信士]背离他[安拉]，",
        "numberInSurah": 162,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3951,
        "text": "注定入火狱[受火刑]者除外。",
        "numberInSurah": 163,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3952,
        "text": "[天使们说]：“我们[天使]每个都有一个周知的位置。",
        "numberInSurah": 164,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3953,
        "text": "我们确是常列班的[如穆斯林礼拜列班一样]。",
        "numberInSurah": 165,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3954,
        "text": "我们确是常赞颂安拉的。”",
        "numberInSurah": 166,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3955,
        "text": "他们[阿拉伯人的异教徒]的确常说：",
        "numberInSurah": 167,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3956,
        "text": "“[在穆圣为圣前]假如我们有前人的教诲，",
        "numberInSurah": 168,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3957,
        "text": "我们一定是安拉特选的仆人。”",
        "numberInSurah": 169,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3958,
        "text": "[现在《古兰经》降示了，穆圣为圣了]，但他们仍不信仰[注][穆圣和《古兰经》]，他们不久将知道[不信仰的后果]。",
        "numberInSurah": 170,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3959,
        "text": "我对我所派遣的仆人们[使者们]的确有言在先：",
        "numberInSurah": 171,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3960,
        "text": "他们确是获胜者。",
        "numberInSurah": 172,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3961,
        "text": "我的军队确是胜利者。",
        "numberInSurah": 173,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3962,
        "text": "所以，你[穆圣]暂时避开他们吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 174,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3963,
        "text": "你观察他们吧！他们不久将看见[刑罚]。",
        "numberInSurah": 175,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3964,
        "text": "难道他们要我早日实现我[对他们]的刑罚吗？",
        "numberInSurah": 176,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3965,
        "text": "当我的刑罚降临他们的庭院时[即降临他们]，被警告者的早晨真恶劣！",
        "numberInSurah": 177,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3966,
        "text": "你暂时避开他们吧！",
        "numberInSurah": 178,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3967,
        "text": "你观察他们吧！他们不久将看见[刑罚]。",
        "numberInSurah": 179,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3968,
        "text": "赞美你的主——尊荣的主超绝！他超绝于他们所妄言的。",
        "numberInSurah": 180,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3969,
        "text": "“赐使者们平安！”",
        "numberInSurah": 181,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 3970,
        "text": "一切赞颂，全归安拉——众世界的主！",
        "numberInSurah": 182,
        "juz": 23,
        "manzil": 6,
        "page": 452,
        "ruku": 390,
        "hizbQuarter": 181,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
